snippet.title: Super Buckyball Tournament Early Alpha Gameplay
snippet.description:
Watch our 8 minutes early development gameplay for Super Buckyball Tournament!

There're 3 characters featured in the gameplay which are Pai, Pink and R47. Stay tuned as we plan to add more characters in the future.

The alpha test will be out soon, join Super Buckyball Tournament official discord server and receive codes to try out the game in early build! https://discord.gg/Bh8tTbD

The steam page for Super Buckyball Tournament is now live, wishlist us and get notified when the game releases in late 2019.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1059110/Super_Buckyball_Tournament/

Follow us on social media to receive the latest updates about the game.

Website: www.superbuckyball.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SuperBuckyBall
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SuperBuckyballtournament
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/superbuckyballtournament
Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SuperBuckyballtourney
